      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Mar 2010 12:26:56 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Slim Thighs Exercises</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Thin Thighs]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[how to thin thighs]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/?p=36</guid>
      <description>If you&amp;#8217;ve ever caught yourself wondering exactly how to thin thighs and firm your lower body, then you may be surprised to find out just how easy it can be to achieve your fitness goals. When it comes to slimming your thighs and tightening your buns, all it really takes to make it happen is [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via: &lt;a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com"&gt;Slim Thighs Exercises&lt;/a&gt; where you can learn how to get slim sexy thighs and a firm tight butt quickly and easily starting today!&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/thin-thighs/how-to-thin-thighs/"&gt;How To Thin Thighs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/slim-thighs-exercises/Slim_Thighs_Exercises-How_To_Thin_Thighs.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>If you&#8217;ve ever caught yourself wondering exactly how to thin thighs and firm your lower body, then you may be surprised to find out just how easy it can be to achieve your fitness goals. When it comes to slimming your thighs and tightening your buns, all it really takes to make it happen is a well thought out plan and some effort on your part.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Primeras poses" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/10496699@N02/4411659657/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2695/4411659657_f4766bb7aa_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Primeras poses" /></a><small> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="Maximo Lopez ( http://afocost.wordpress.com)" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/10496699@N02/4411659657/" target="_blank">Maximo Lopez ( http://afocost.wordpress.com)</a></small></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">One of the first things that you need to take into account to thin your thighs is your nutrition plan.  While most women (and men for that matter) resort to a haphazard unorganized style of eating, it&#8217;s important to realize that a clean and healthy diet will account for up to 80% of your fat loss / weight loss / thigh slimming goals. Listed below are three thigh slimming nutrition tips to help you get moving towards your slim thighs goals today!</p>
<p>1.) Focus on eating 5 -6 smaller meals throughout the day.  Instead of focusing on eating only 2 or 3 big meals each day, give your metabolism a major boost by tapping into the &#8220;thermic effect of food&#8221;.  By eating smaller more frequent meals throughout the day, your body will begin to expend more energy just digesting the nutrients.  This gives you an advantage when it comes to slimming your thighs.</p>
<p>2.) Eat more fiber.  Fiber is a proven weight loss food and it&#8217;s healthy for you!  The recommended daily allowance of fiber is    for average women.  Most women don&#8217;t even come close to eating this quantity of fat melting fiber. Start out by making it a point to eat the recommended daily allowance for a few weeks , then try to eat a bit more. This will help you firm your buns at record pace!</p>
<p>Although it&#8217;s not highly publicized, fiber is one of the key points of emphasis for the contestants in T.V.&#8217;s Biggest Loser.</p>
<p>3.)  Drink plenty of water.  When you are trying to tone your thighs and slim your lower body, water can be one of your best friends! When you body is properly hydrated, not only will it run more efficiently, but your body will retain less water.  This will help you get that muscular toned look in your thighs and buns.  Regardless of how much fat you&#8217;re able to lose, if you&#8217;re retaining a lot of water, then your legs will look mushy and soft!</p>
<p>Well, that&#8217;s pretty much how to thin thighs and firm your lower body by implementing a few basic nutrition tips.  Simple and easy &#8211; yet very effective for achieving the toned athletic thighs that most women would die for!  Make it a habit to incorporate each of these thigh slimming nutrition tips into your daily nutrition plan and watch as your thighs start to slim.</p>
<p>This post via: <a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com">Slim Thighs Exercises</a> where you can learn how to get slim sexy thighs and a firm tight butt quickly and easily starting today!<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/thin-thighs/how-to-thin-thighs/">How To Thin Thighs</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
