      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Mar 2010 23:21:55 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Slim Thighs Exercises</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Thin Thighs]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[how to get skinny thighs]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/?p=8</guid>
      <description>Most women would like to know how to get skinny things and form buns safely and naturally without having to spend hours in the gym each day. While there is definitely a lot of conflicting advice and downright scams floating around out there, the truth of the matter is that a firmer sexier lower body [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via: &lt;a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com"&gt;Slim Thighs Exercises&lt;/a&gt; where you can learn how to get slim sexy thighs and a firm tight butt quickly and easily starting today!&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/thin-thighs/how-to-get-skinny-thighs/"&gt;How To Get Skinny Thighs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/slim-thighs-exercises/Slim_Thighs_Exercises-How_To_Get_Skinny_Thighs.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Most women would like to know how to get skinny things and form buns safely and naturally without having to spend hours in the gym each day.  While there is definitely a lot of conflicting advice and downright scams floating around out there, the truth of the matter is that a firmer sexier lower body can be achieved without too much effort on your part.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="WWLT: Tracker Jacket and Tracker Tight Crops" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/30011527@N05/4257609022/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2681/4257609022_9fafc8a1b8_m.jpg" border="0" alt="WWLT: Tracker Jacket and Tracker Tight Crops" /></a><small> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="lululemon athletica" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/30011527@N05/4257609022/" target="_blank">lululemon athletica</a></small></p>
<p>If you&#8217;re wanting to slim your thighs, hips and buns without spending hour upon hour in the gym, then you need to learn how to piece together an efficient fat burning workout.  Whether you prefer aerobic exercise or strength training, the best approach for whipping your lower body into shape is a combination of the two style of exercise.</p>
<p><strong>Strength training serves as a way to&#8230;</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Increase you bone density</li>
<li>Increase Your muscle mass</li>
<li>Boost your metabolism</li>
<li>Strengthen your muscles</li>
<li>Burn fat</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Aerobics / Cardio serves as a way for you to&#8230;</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Burn more calories</li>
<li>Increase your cardiovascular health</li>
<li>Tone and firm the muscles of your hips, thighs and buns</li>
<li>Boost your metabolism</li>
<li>Increase you overall level of fitness</li>
</ul>
<p>So if you want to know how to get skinny thighs quickly, the answer is to simply combine strength training with cardio during the same workout.  This style of training is known  as high intensity interval training.</p>
<p><strong>In order to make H.I.I.T. training work for you&#8230;</strong></p>
<p>1.) Pick 2 full body free weight exercises</p>
<p>2.) Pick 1 type of cardiovascular exercise</p>
<p>3.) Perform 2 minute intervals of your cardio exercise followed by 2 minute intervals of your weight training exercise with minimal rest between sets.</p>
<p>4.) Start by performing 3 full sets at each station, then progress to 4-5 sets as you level of fitness improves.</p>
<p>This is a great outline for an effective fat burning, thigh slimming workout that is guaranteed to help you get skinny thighs and a sexy lower body.</p>
<p>This post via: <a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com">Slim Thighs Exercises</a> where you can learn how to get slim sexy thighs and a firm tight butt quickly and easily starting today!<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/thin-thighs/how-to-get-skinny-thighs/">How To Get Skinny Thighs</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
