    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Get Thin Hips Today!</title>
      <link>http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/hip-exercises/thin-hips/</link>
      <comments>http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/hip-exercises/thin-hips/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2009 13:03:51 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Slim Thighs Exercises</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Hip Exercises]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Thin Thighs]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[firm buns]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[sexy thighs]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[thin hips]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/?p=15</guid>
      <description>If you&amp;#8217;re looking for thin hips and sexy thighs and firm buns, then absolutely have to make daily exercise a regular habit. With fad diets and infomercials promising quick fix solutions for weight loss and flabby thighs, it can be hard to figure out exactly what works when it comes to shaping your lower body. [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via: &lt;a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com"&gt;Slim Thighs Exercises&lt;/a&gt; where you can learn how to get slim sexy thighs and a firm tight butt quickly and easily starting today!&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/hip-exercises/thin-hips/"&gt;Get Thin Hips Today!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/slim-thighs-exercises/Slim_Thighs_Exercises-Get_Thin_Hips_Today.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>If you&#8217;re looking for thin hips and sexy thighs and firm buns, then absolutely have to make daily exercise a regular habit.  With fad diets and infomercials promising quick fix solutions for weight loss and flabby thighs, it can be hard to figure out exactly what works when it comes to shaping your lower body.</p>
<p>While gimmicks do work for some women, chances are the results fade quickly after only a few weeks of initial success.  <a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/buttmakeover">The truth about getting thin hips and firm buns</a> is that you have to put in some hard work in order to get a sexy lower body.  While it would be great if you could just think about how much you wanted to thin your thighs and hips and watch it happen before your very eyes, it&#8217;s just not realistic to believe that this can happen.</p>
<h2><span style="font-size: medium;">Get Thin Hips With Daily Exercise </span></h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Its so soft..." href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/23118985@N03/3597163044/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter" style="border: 0pt none;" title="Sexy Thin Hips!" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3603/3597163044_a749f223b4_m.jpg" border="0" alt="Its so soft..." width="195" height="240" /></a><small><a title="Attribution-NoDerivs License" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/2.0/" target="_blank"><img src="http://173.192.120.91/~nicka241/slimthighsexercises.com/wp-content/plugins/photo-dropper/images/cc.png" border="0" alt="Creative Commons License" width="16" height="16" align="absmiddle" /></a> <a href="http://www.photodropper.com/photos/" target="_blank">photo</a> credit: <a title="chrisbastian44" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/23118985@N03/3597163044/" target="_blank">chrisbastian44</a></small></p>
<p>When it comes to slimming your thighs, firming your buns and achieving thin hips, there is no greater ally than a simple daily exercise session. Sure you can find programs that are based around fad diets, but long lasting weight loss results stem from regular exercise combined with a nutritious balanced diet.</p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>Here&#8217;s How The Fat Loss Process Really Works&#8230; </strong></span></p>
<p>In order to burn fat, firm your lower body and thin your hips, you will need to focus on creating a calorie deficit that is somewhere in the ballpark of 3000 &#8211; 4000 calories each week.  This will translate into an approximate fat weight loss of 1lb. If you would like to shed 2lbs a week, then you will need to create a calorie deficit that is double that value (approx. 6000 &#8211; 8000 calories per week).</p>
<p>A calorie deficit is simply putting your body into a position to expend more energy than you take in each day. There are a few ways to accomplish this goal, but the best approach is to combine daily exercise with a well balanced and nutritious diet.  If you focus on performing some type of exercise for 20 &#8211; 40 minutes each day, then you will be going a long way towards creating an energy deficit without even altering what you eat!</p>
<p>If you combine your daily exercise session with a simple calorie reduction of 250 calories per day, then you will be on track to lose 1 lbs of fat each week.   This simple lifestyle change will definitely allow you to get sexy thin hips and firm thighs quickly, easily and naturally!</p>
<p>This post via: <a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com">Slim Thighs Exercises</a> where you can learn how to get slim sexy thighs and a firm tight butt quickly and easily starting today!<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/hip-exercises/thin-hips/">Get Thin Hips Today!</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
      <wfw:commentRss>http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/hip-exercises/thin-hips/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
      <slash:comments>12</slash:comments>
      <enclosure url="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/slim-thighs-exercises/Slim_Thighs_Exercises-Get_Thin_Hips_Today.mp3" length="1308508" type="audio/mpeg" />
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Why You Should Perform Thigh Squats</title>
      <link>http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/thigh-exercises/thigh-squats/</link>
      <comments>http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/thigh-exercises/thigh-squats/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2009 11:24:26 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Slim Thighs Exercises</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Thigh Exercises]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[thigh squats]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/?p=131</guid>
      <description>Thigh squats are one of the most effective exercises that you can do in order to slim your thighs and firm up your lower body.  While squats are traditionally thought of as a basic leg exercise, most people don&amp;#8217;t know that in addition to the thighs, squats also work the muscles in your butt as [...]&lt;p&gt;This post via: &lt;a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com"&gt;Slim Thighs Exercises&lt;/a&gt; where you can learn how to get slim sexy thighs and a firm tight butt quickly and easily starting today!&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.slimthighsexercises.com/thigh-exercises/thigh-squats/"&gt;Why You Should Perform Thigh Squats&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/slim-thighs-exercises/Slim_Thighs_Exercises-Why_You_Should_Perform_Thigh_Squats.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Thigh squats are one of the most effective exercises that you can do in order to slim your thighs and firm up your lower body.  While squats are traditionally thought of as a basic leg exercise, most people don&#8217;t know that in addition to the thighs, squats also work the muscles in your butt as well as every other muscle in your lower body.</p>
<h2><span style="font-size: large;">Why You Should Perform Thigh Squats</span></h2>
<p>If you are looking to slim your thighs quickly and efficiently, then you must perform squats. There are a few reasons why this is such an effective exercise for lower body fat and toning your thighs and buns, so I&#8217;ll highlight a few of them below&#8230;</p>
<p>1.) The muscles in your thighs, hips, butt and calves are some of the biggest muscles in your entire body. Because of their size, these muscles are also stronger than the other muscles in your body. When you  perform a free weight exercise like thigh squats, you are requiring the biggest and strongest muscles in your body to work very hard &#8211; this type of activity burn  a lot of calories!</p>
<p>AS you know, in order to burn body fat, you need to expend (burn) more calories than you take in on a regular basis. Squats when performed as a regular addition to your slim thighs workouts can contribute quite a bit towards creating the all important calorie deficit.</p>
<p>2.) Not only do thigh squats require an enormous amount of energy to perform, but they also target all of the muscles in your lower body.  Since your goal is to slim your thighs quickly, easily and naturally, doesn&#8217;t it just make good sense to try and get the biggest bang for your buck with each and every workout?</p>
<p>3.) Weight bearing exercises like thigh squats have been shown to increase the density of your bones.  If you combine regular weight bearing exercises with a calcium supplement, then you can really go a long way to ensure that your bones stay in good health for the rest of your life!</p>
<p>So not only do squats allow you to shape your thighs, hips and buns while also burning fat, but they also allow you to reduce your risk of developing osteoporosis later in life!  This alone should be enough reason to incorporate thigh squats into your fitness mix right away!</p>
<h3><span style="font-size: large;">Types of Thigh Squats</span></h3>
<p>There are a few different types of squats that you can work into your slim thigh workouts in order to keep things from getting too repetitive. Here is a list of different types of squats that target your thighs, hips and butt&#8230;</p>
<ul>
<li>Barbell Squat</li>
<li>DB Squat</li>
<li>Wall Squats</li>
<li>Single Leg Squats (also known as Bulgarian squats)</li>
<li>Bodyweight squats</li>
<li>Front Squats</li>
</ul>
